1. *Pratili* su ga svi danima. (They followed him for days.)
2. *Pratila* je radoznalo njegovu priču. (She followed his story with curiosity.)
3. On je *pratio* njenu vokalnu liniju. (He followed her vocal line.)
4. *Pratimo* korake naših prethodnika. (We follow the footsteps of our predecessors.)
5. Ona je *pratila* njegove savete. (She followed his advice.)
6. Nije *pratio* nikoga u tom trenutku. (He wasn't following anyone at that moment.)